tivars have been produced, particularly of cantaloupes.","wiki"),("lemon","5","The ___, Citrus limon  Osbeck, is a species of small evergreen tree in the flowering plant family Rutaceae, native to South Asia, primarily North eastern India. Its fruits are round in shape.","wiki");